title: You Are Not Broken
itunes:title: You Are Not Broken
description:
Episode 642 - You are not broken. This is truth, but so many people still walk around thinking that there is something wrong with them. They think that because of their past or because of what someone else did to them that they are not whole, or that there is something missing in them that others have. In this episode, I am going to prove to you that there is nothing wrong and that you are perfect just the way you are. Follow me on Instagram at https://www.instagram.com/robdialjr/
